{"tid":1681064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩行動可以針對黑警/狗車","createTime":"2019-10-29T07:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T07:45:46.000Z","uid":5739,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbeb82af96987a29a6796d6603461f684fe7b28","tid":1681064,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"有時喺街零零舍舍見到幾隻狗<br />\n或者一兩架狗車<br />\n有冇啲咩可以即刻做到？<br />\n<br />\n有時啲哨channel又有報邊度有狗有車<br />\n其實我哋可唔可以利用依啲資訊去即時做啲嘢？<br />\n<br />\n另外老豆揾仔起咗咁多底，又有咩實際行動做到？<br />\n<br />\n利用依啲資訊係佢哋在明我哋在暗<br />\n會唔會比大型遊行集會直接對峙有效率？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"84c5d07610793f2d48a5aca8a5206aa3333e5385","tid":1681064,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"油"},{"pid":"53c98121d19c074cab5eafb0155c80929d8f873d","tid":1681064,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac8bd326ecd7a3f42bfdf16153f5cb9d0dc9030","tid":1681064,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d053061dd2e7a2d8eec5d10cdf1210ad90c2ccea","tid":1681064,"uid":134602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"Help push<br />\n<br />\n【突發】林鄭聽朝喺港交所有個講座<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1680991/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1680991/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"931bba00f5a746386cc9a9e85611181772bd8c40","tid":1681064,"uid":202720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T07:43:11